{"type":"text","timestamp":1775862345069,"sessionID":"ses_286621cb8ffel5WbNo5U839Mdp","part":{"id":"prt_d79a4c6ab001EDKaa0yfnbuXPx","messageID":"msg_d79a0187e001oDhFAx7YAlAPFG","sessionID":"ses_286621cb8ffel5WbNo5U839Mdp","type":"text","text":"The delta-spec.md for AR-011 has been successfully created with comprehensive GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios. Here's a summary of the specification:\n\n## AR-011: Router JWT 认证与签发 - Delta Specification\n\n### Requirements Covered (7 major requirements with 27+ scenarios):\n\n1. **RSA Key Pair Generation** (3 scenarios)\n   - New key pair generation\n   - Secure random source usage\n   - Error handling for generation failures\n\n2. **JWT Token Generation and Signing** (6 scenarios)\n   - Custom claims generation\n   - Standard claims (exp, iat, iss) auto-population\n   - RS256 algorithm usage\n   - Signing failure handling\n   - Configurable expiration\n\n3. **RSA Key PEM Encoding** (3 scenarios)\n   - Public key PKIX PEM export\n   - Private key PKCS#1 PEM export\n   - UTF-8 encoding for Kubernetes Secret storage\n\n4. **Kubernetes Secret Key Storage** (7 scenarios)\n   - New secret creation\n   - Existing key loading\n   - Non-cluster environment fallback\n   - Kubernetes client failure handling\n   - Secret creation failures\n   - Malformed key data handling\n\n5. **JWT Key Loading from PEM** (3 scenarios)\n   - Valid PEM parsing\n   - Invalid PEM block handling\n   - Invalid PKCS#1 content handling\n\n6. **Namespace Configuration** (2 scenarios)\n   - Default namespace behavior\n   - Environment variable override\n\n7. **Token Validation Support** (3 scenarios)\n   - Valid signature verification\n   - Invalid signature rejection\n   - Expired token rejection\n\n### Key Components Documented:\n- **JWTManager struct** with all methods\n- **Constants**: rsaKeySize (2048), jwtExpiration (5min), identitySecretName, etc.\n- **Dependencies**: golang-jwt/jwt/v5, k8s.io/client-go, and crypto libraries\n- **File Index**: pkg/router/jwt.go, errors.go, config.go\n- **Migration Notes**: RBAC requirements, key rotation procedure\n- **8 Acceptance Criteria** for validation","time":{"start":1775862345068,"end":1775862345068}}}
